290
00:19:46,880 --> 00:19:47,599
When I wake up,

291
00:19:48,599 --> 00:19:49,079
I will teach you.

292
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:50,759
What will you teach me?

293
00:19:51,559 --> 00:19:52,039
Medicine.

294
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:54,079
Medicine.

295
00:19:56,640 --> 00:19:58,119
Just pick one.

296
00:20:08,440 --> 00:20:08,880
Dig it out.

297
00:20:16,359 --> 00:20:16,839
Alright.

298
00:20:17,759 --> 00:20:18,240
Open it.

299
00:20:18,519 --> 00:20:19,039
Alright.

300
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:23,359
Why don't you ask me the reason?

301
00:20:24,119 --> 00:20:24,720
For what?

302
00:20:26,119 --> 00:20:27,319
Why do I ask you to open the coffin?

303
00:20:27,880 --> 00:20:29,000
I should know human's body first.

304
00:20:29,400 --> 00:20:30,480
And then get a dead body to dissect.

305
00:20:30,720 --> 00:20:31,759
This is the first step for my study.

306
00:20:32,079 --> 00:20:33,000
That's normal.

307
00:20:35,799 --> 00:20:36,240
Open it.

308
00:20:44,640 --> 00:20:45,640
It's still fresh.

309
00:20:46,359 --> 00:20:46,839
Cut it open.

310
00:20:47,440 --> 00:20:48,440
Check out the cause of death.

311
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:49,319
Cut it.

312
00:20:56,079 --> 00:20:57,079
Are you afraid?

313
00:20:57,759 --> 00:20:58,559
There are too many bacteria here.

314
00:20:59,079 --> 00:21:00,400
I should get protected.

315
00:21:00,880 --> 00:21:01,680
What is bacteria?

316
00:21:03,160 --> 00:21:04,200
I mean it's dirty.

317
00:21:04,279 --> 00:21:05,720
I'd better put on a pair of gloves at least.

318
00:21:07,519 --> 00:21:08,880
When you cut a body open,

319
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:10,759
you should use your hands to get every detail.

320
00:21:11,599 --> 00:21:12,559
It's not convenient to dissect a body

321
00:21:14,559 --> 00:21:16,720
when you wear a pair of gloves.

322
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:19,640
It's not what you wear in winter.

323
00:21:20,319 --> 00:21:22,079
The gloves for operation are very thin.

324
00:21:23,079 --> 00:21:24,680
They are close fitting, do you know that?

325
00:21:25,759 --> 00:21:26,759
About the gloves you just mentioned,

326
00:21:26,759 --> 00:21:28,079
I have never heard about it before.

327
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:30,000
After the dissection,

328
00:21:30,480 --> 00:21:31,960
you can wash your hands.

329
00:21:41,039 --> 00:21:42,079
Uncle Wuzhu is awesome.

330
00:21:42,720 --> 00:21:45,400
He even could compete with the Four Great Masters.

331
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:50,000
If it were not for Wuzhu's low profile,

332
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:52,359
he would be famous

333
00:21:52,759 --> 00:21:54,000
and become the fifth great master

334
00:21:54,519 --> 00:21:56,200
in the world.

335
00:21:57,519 --> 00:21:59,440
What's the relationship between
my mom and Uncle Wuzhu?

336
00:22:00,359 --> 00:22:03,279
He was your mother's servant.

337
00:22:04,400 --> 00:22:05,799
Well, my mom must be more awesome!

338
00:22:06,720 --> 00:22:09,359
Your mother actually was unparalleled in the world.

339
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:11,319
How did she die that year?

340
00:22:12,039 --> 00:22:12,720
I can't tell you.

341
00:22:13,160 --> 00:22:14,359
Just tell me a little.

342
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:16,160
You talk too much.

343
00:22:16,720 --> 00:22:17,880
You can't bear it, can you?

344
00:22:30,519 --> 00:22:31,000
You...

345
00:22:31,400 --> 00:22:33,480
There is something that you can't bear?

346
00:22:35,680 --> 00:22:36,440
Teacher,

347
00:22:37,119 --> 00:22:38,480
I am still a kid.

348
00:22:45,000 --> 00:22:45,880
Uncle.

349
00:22:46,720 --> 00:22:48,720
I have dissected the body for a whole night.

350
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:51,720
And you just cook this for me?

351
00:22:52,480 --> 00:22:52,880
Right.

352
00:22:54,519 --> 00:22:55,240
Will you put some ingredients into it?

353
00:22:56,400 --> 00:22:56,920
No.

354
00:22:58,880 --> 00:23:00,400
Did my mom teach you how to cook it?

355
00:23:06,359 --> 00:23:07,200
What do you want to say?

356
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:09,720
What kind of person my mom is?

357
00:23:11,039 --> 00:23:12,240
Her name is Ye Qingmei.

358
00:23:12,799 --> 00:23:13,400
What else?

359
00:23:22,119 --> 00:23:22,839
The others...

360
00:23:23,880 --> 00:23:24,359
I've forgotten all of them.

361
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:32,279
You gave me

362
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:33,640
this secret skills about vitality Qi.

363
00:23:33,799 --> 00:23:34,440
Do you remember it?

364
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:37,480
It's your mother who gave it to you.

365
00:23:39,119 --> 00:23:39,920
I have practiced it

366
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:41,279
