367
00:23:41,839 --> 00:23:43,759
I can't control it. It's really overbearing.

368
00:23:44,559 --> 00:23:45,000
Uncle.

369
00:23:46,640 --> 00:23:47,839
Does it have a name?

370
00:23:48,279 --> 00:23:48,720
Yes.

371
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:49,960
What is it?

372
00:23:50,680 --> 00:23:51,640
“Overbearing Vitality Qi”.

373
00:23:53,039 --> 00:23:53,680
It seems like

374
00:23:53,680 --> 00:23:55,279
you name it just now?

375
00:23:57,480 --> 00:23:59,240
If I can't control it well,

376
00:23:59,839 --> 00:24:01,279
I'm afraid it will do harm to my body.

377
00:24:02,559 --> 00:24:03,119
Uncle.

378
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:05,200
How can I practice it?

379
00:24:17,960 --> 00:24:18,480
You don't know?

380
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:20,839
I haven't practiced it.

381
00:24:22,720 --> 00:24:25,039
But my teacher told me you are super awesome.

382
00:24:26,960 --> 00:24:27,720
Not bad.

383
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:30,920
Did my mother die of anger because of you?

384
00:24:31,960 --> 00:24:32,440
I've forgotten all of them.

385
00:24:33,720 --> 00:24:35,000
Well, about my problem,

386
00:24:35,000 --> 00:24:36,400
what on earth should I do?

387
00:24:38,400 --> 00:24:39,240
Finish the radish

388
00:24:40,920 --> 00:24:41,480
and follow me.

389
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:49,160
To where?

390
00:24:52,559 --> 00:24:53,680
Use the Qi

391
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:55,640
and fill it to your feet.

392
00:24:55,960 --> 00:24:57,200
The speed will be faster.

393
00:25:20,279 --> 00:25:21,160
I haven't practiced Kungfu

394
00:25:21,880 --> 00:25:23,000
and don't know how to use the Qi.

395
00:25:23,960 --> 00:25:25,920
So I find out a way

396
00:25:26,319 --> 00:25:27,599
to practice your skills.

397
00:25:27,960 --> 00:25:28,720
What is it?

398
00:25:29,079 --> 00:25:29,799
I will beat you.

399
00:25:31,119 --> 00:25:31,799
And then?

400
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:32,799
You dodge.

401
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:34,839
And this is your way?

402
00:25:35,839 --> 00:25:36,839
