403
00:25:50,359 --> 00:25:51,000
Once again.

404
00:26:24,319 --> 00:26:25,319
It's okay.

405
00:26:26,480 --> 00:26:27,880
Kids like sleeping.

406
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:47,200
Think about it. What poison is it?

407
00:26:48,799 --> 00:26:50,079
When were you poisoned?

408
00:26:51,079 --> 00:26:52,400
And how?

409
00:26:55,400 --> 00:26:57,599
When I was picking up the chopsticks,

410
00:26:58,240 --> 00:26:59,240
you poisoned me.

411
00:27:01,319 --> 00:27:02,440
It tastes astringent,

412
00:27:03,279 --> 00:27:05,880
so you mixed it in the edible wild herbs.

413
00:27:11,759 --> 00:27:13,079
You can choose one

414
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:14,880
as I teach you.

415
00:27:28,839 --> 00:27:29,559
No.

416
00:27:40,440 --> 00:27:40,920
What about...

417
00:27:41,839 --> 00:27:43,319
Take it if you make your decision.

418
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:44,480
... this one?

419
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:45,880
You will know after taking it.

420
00:28:06,920 --> 00:28:07,440
What's wrong?

421
00:28:11,440 --> 00:28:12,599
Teacher, what happened to me?

422
00:28:14,599 --> 00:28:15,759
Your choice is wrong.

423
00:28:17,480 --> 00:28:18,799
But the smell in the other bottles

424
00:28:18,799 --> 00:28:19,839
is not right.

425
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:22,799
I told you to choose one bottle,

426
00:28:23,279 --> 00:28:24,279
but I didn't say

427
00:28:24,480 --> 00:28:25,640
the cure was among them.

428
00:28:25,920 --> 00:28:26,680
Teacher, you are too...

429
00:28:28,079 --> 00:28:29,359
You went too far.

430
00:28:29,359 --> 00:28:30,279
Why didn't you say you went too far

431
00:28:30,279 --> 00:28:31,400
when you knocked me out?

432
00:28:32,559 --> 00:28:33,359
If you have any problems with that,

433
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:34,839
you can poison me.

434
00:28:35,119 --> 00:28:36,200
If you can make it,

435
00:28:36,599 --> 00:28:37,640
then we can finish the apprenticeship.

436
00:28:53,559 --> 00:28:55,680
It's my turn to teach him today.

437
00:28:57,640 --> 00:28:59,119
Let me teach him today.

438
00:29:30,799 --> 00:29:31,440
Uncle.

439
00:29:32,039 --> 00:29:33,880
I think I can't make it forever.

440
00:29:34,480 --> 00:29:35,480
You just need time.

441
00:29:38,079 --> 00:29:38,920
My teacher said

442
00:29:39,480 --> 00:29:41,279
you were on the same level
with the Four Great Masters.

443
00:29:41,559 --> 00:29:42,240
Kind of.

444
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:43,119
Have you fought with them?

445
00:29:43,119 --> 00:29:44,000
Not all of them.

446
00:29:44,279 --> 00:29:45,000
Who won?

447
00:29:45,920 --> 00:29:46,559
I made it even.

448
00:29:47,400 --> 00:29:49,480
They are the most powerful four men in the world.

449
00:29:49,960 --> 00:29:51,160
You have never learned Kungfu,

450
00:29:51,319 --> 00:29:53,480
how can you make it even with them?

451
00:29:53,839 --> 00:29:55,880
If only you are fast

452
00:29:56,079 --> 00:29:56,839
and strong enough.

453
00:29:56,960 --> 00:29:58,960
How powerful should you be to
match with those great masters?

454
00:30:02,960 --> 00:30:03,559
Uncle Wuzhu.

455
00:30:12,839 --> 00:30:15,039
Uncle, in the front is a cliff.

456
00:30:15,359 --> 00:30:16,440
If you could be so powerful as me,

457
00:30:16,759 --> 00:30:17,480
and strong enough.

458
00:30:28,079 --> 00:30:28,680
Uncle.

459
00:30:41,599 --> 00:30:43,640
Is he a real human?

460
00:30:47,920 --> 00:30:48,920
Teacher, please have a seat.

461
00:30:50,079 --> 00:30:51,480
This is the poisoned tea I just made.

462
00:30:51,720 --> 00:30:52,400
Please have a taste.

463
00:31:15,000 --> 00:31:16,440
Tharm-cutting flower again?

464
00:31:16,839 --> 00:31:18,200
But I didn't put it in the tea.

465
00:31:18,519 --> 00:31:19,519
How did you make it?

466
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:21,720
The inner part is toxic

467
00:31:22,839 --> 00:31:23,880
but the skin is not.

468
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:26,920
Just think about it.

469
00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:46,079
Gotcha!

470
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:47,519
What poison is it?

471
00:31:48,519 --> 00:31:51,160
It's not the poison but time.

472
00:31:51,559 --> 00:31:52,319
These days,

473
00:31:52,799 --> 00:31:55,519
you had a lot of good tonics.

474
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:58,480
Teacher, you are not poisoned.

475
00:31:58,920 --> 00:32:00,400
You just had too many tonics and

476
00:32:00,720 --> 00:32:01,640
you have too prosperous qi and blood.

477
00:32:03,240 --> 00:32:04,519
You are so smart.

478
00:32:06,079 --> 00:32:07,160
Now my apprenticeship is finished?

479
00:32:08,559 --> 00:32:10,319
I can finish the apprenticeship
if I poison you successfully?

480
00:32:10,680 --> 00:32:11,319
Right.

481
00:32:12,839 --> 00:32:14,640
I made it!

482
00:32:34,279 --> 00:32:36,759
All good things come to an end. I should go now.

483
00:32:38,160 --> 00:32:38,799
Stop here.

484
00:32:41,319 --> 00:32:42,079
These years,

485
00:32:43,240 --> 00:32:45,119
the only person who I can completely trust

486
00:32:46,119 --> 00:32:47,240
is Uncle Wuzhu.

487
00:32:48,599 --> 00:32:49,920
