488
00:32:52,359 --> 00:32:53,480
But now I have another people who I can trust.

489
00:33:00,000 --> 00:33:01,279
Don't forget you have such a naughty student

490
00:33:01,279 --> 00:33:02,680
like me in Danzhou.

491
00:33:06,759 --> 00:33:07,240
Here you are.

492
00:33:11,519 --> 00:33:13,200
It's the token of Director-General
of the investigator's office.

493
00:33:14,000 --> 00:33:15,319
The Head asked me to give it to you.

494
00:33:16,359 --> 00:33:18,599
Did he know me?

495
00:33:19,759 --> 00:33:22,039
He knows your mother.

496
00:33:23,599 --> 00:33:24,400
And I have something for you.

497
00:33:38,039 --> 00:33:39,039
It's made of lamb intestine.

498
00:33:39,799 --> 00:33:41,599
You can put it on

499
00:33:41,799 --> 00:33:42,640
when you dissect bodies or test the poisons.

500
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:43,799
Okay.

501
00:33:46,720 --> 00:33:47,279
I like it.

502
00:33:50,720 --> 00:33:52,759
If I met you earlier,

503
00:33:54,319 --> 00:33:56,519
I may choose another way.

504
00:33:59,000 --> 00:33:59,599
Excuse me?

505
00:34:01,279 --> 00:34:02,799
I will take care of you when you are old
and give proper burial after your death.

506
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:27,960
He left and it turns out to be a good thing.

507
00:34:28,920 --> 00:34:30,079
He will stay in Danzhou.

508
00:34:31,079 --> 00:34:32,920
he will attract people's attention

509
00:34:33,079 --> 00:34:34,199
from the capital city.

510
00:34:36,119 --> 00:34:37,280
Am I in danger?

511
00:34:39,440 --> 00:34:40,239
If the red-armor

512
00:34:41,159 --> 00:34:42,400
knights

513
00:34:42,760 --> 00:34:44,760
appear in the street here,

514
00:34:46,519 --> 00:34:47,840
the real danger

515
00:34:50,840 --> 00:34:51,880
will come.

516
00:34:53,719 --> 00:34:55,119
Who are the red-armor knights?

517
00:35:04,199 --> 00:35:05,840
Young Master Fan Xian, what are you doing?

518
00:35:06,199 --> 00:35:07,519
I am waiting for the red-armor knights.

519
00:35:07,880 --> 00:35:09,119
Who are the red-armor knights?

520
00:35:09,599 --> 00:35:10,320
You don't understand.

521
00:36:10,079 --> 00:36:10,760
Young Master Fan Xian,

522
00:36:11,079 --> 00:36:12,199
Are you still waiting for the red-armor knights?

523
00:37:18,119 --> 00:37:19,639
These people are here to escort me to the capital city?

524
00:37:20,800 --> 00:37:21,679
Who asked them here?

525
00:37:22,800 --> 00:37:24,159
Your father, of course.

526
00:37:25,400 --> 00:37:26,639
I have refused him.

527
00:37:28,039 --> 00:37:29,840
The capital city is not a good place.

528
00:37:31,199 --> 00:37:32,639
Your mother died there.

529
00:37:34,519 --> 00:37:35,559
You can live longer

530
00:37:36,880 --> 00:37:38,159
if you stay here.

531
00:37:38,559 --> 00:37:40,159
But they are kneeling out of the door.

532
00:37:41,639 --> 00:37:42,480
Leave them alone.

533
00:37:44,280 --> 00:37:45,199
If they kneel there till they die,

534
00:37:46,159 --> 00:37:47,480
just bury them.

535
00:38:20,159 --> 00:38:20,679
Uncle,

536
00:38:21,920 --> 00:38:23,559
should I go to the capital city?

537
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:26,079
I remember your mom doing business

538
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:27,039
in the capital city back then.

539
00:38:28,360 --> 00:38:28,840
What else?

540
00:38:29,840 --> 00:38:30,519
I can't remember.

541
00:38:37,000 --> 00:38:38,119
So you mean

542
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:39,199
I should go.

543
00:38:40,639 --> 00:38:42,760
To go or not to go, it's up to you.

544
00:38:47,920 --> 00:38:49,079
My mom was killed in the capital city.

545
00:38:49,320 --> 00:38:50,320
Are those killers still alive?

546
00:38:50,960 --> 00:38:51,679
I have no idea.

547
00:38:56,599 --> 00:38:57,679
I want to go to the capital city.

548
00:38:59,159 --> 00:39:00,880
What if it's dangerous?

549
00:39:02,599 --> 00:39:03,280
Whatever you like.

550
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:12,599
What are you looking at?

551
00:39:14,519 --> 00:39:16,159
I've been wondering recently.

552
00:39:17,599 --> 00:39:19,280
Will your face remain young

553
00:39:20,280 --> 00:39:21,599
