554
00:39:39,360 --> 00:39:39,800
Grandma!

555
00:39:41,920 --> 00:39:42,480
Madam!

556
00:39:44,599 --> 00:39:45,400
Those soldiers

557
00:39:45,400 --> 00:39:47,000
