571
00:40:26,400 --> 00:40:27,119
Anything wrong?

572
00:40:30,599 --> 00:40:31,000
Nothing.

573
00:40:35,760 --> 00:40:36,159
Grandma!

574
00:40:36,800 --> 00:40:38,159
